* In 1993, the replicated version of ''Battlezone'' was included in [[Microsoft Arcade]] for PC with Windows 3.1 and Windows 95, and Mac version for Apple Macintosh.
* ''Battlezone 2000'' for the [[Atari Lynx]] was released in 1995.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://atariage.com/software_page.php?SoftwareLabelID=1870|title=Atari Lynx - Battlezone 2000|website=AtariAge}}</ref>
