* A re-imagining of ''Battlezone'' was developed by [[Paradigm Entertainment]] and released for the [[PlayStation Portable]].<ref>{{cite web | author=Dobson, Jason | date=May 4, 2006 | title=Pre-E3: Battlezone Re-imagined, Charlotte's Web, Codemasters Finds Bliss | url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/9175/PreE3_Battlezone_Reimagined_Charlottes_Web_Codemasters_Finds_Bliss.php | website=[[Gamasutra]] | access-date=2010-01-29}}</ref>
